enb_long_title: Ninth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
sentences: Review of methodological work: AUSTRALIA noted the value of the synthesis of views on a future work programme on methodological work and, with the EU, stressed the need for a data interface.
The US highlighted the need to prioritize important issues, and take into account capacity, expertise, and financial considerations.
SBSTA agreed to convene a contact group to discuss these issues.
